biting Seyfert-like optical emission line ratios, and the\nremaining galaxies classified either as composite objects (2/9) or starburst\n(1/9). (Abridged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Sep 2001 03:55:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
